description: The Pink Cupcake is baking up delicious cupcakes, cake pops, and cupcake cakes just for you! Light, fluffy, and oh so sweet, there's nothing quite so nice as freshly made cupcakes, and The Pink Cupcake are experts at making the very best! Perfect for any occasion or even just walking around town, The Pink Cupcake is your number one place for delicious baked goodness!
name: The Pink Cupcake
